              <a href="/experts/michael-mills-phd"><img src="https://cdn.psychologytoday.com/sites/default/files/styles/profile_thumb/public/-3_24.jpg?itok=uCB8D_uL" width="104" height="130" alt="Michael Mills Ph.D." title="Michael Mills Ph.D." /></a>            </div>
