            <h2 class="page__title">How to Avoid Population Overshoot and Collapse</h2>

      
              <div class="blog-subtitle">
          Manipulating psychological adaptations to help to prevent ecological overshoot.        </div>
        <div class="fb-like-button">
          <div id="fb-root"></div><script src="https://cdn.psychologytoday.com/sites/all/modules/custom/pt_facebook/js/pt_facebook.like.js"></script><div class="fb-like" data-href="https://www.psychologytoday.com/blog/the-how-and-why-sex-differences/201111/how-avoid-population-overshoot-and-collapse" data-layout="button_count" data-action="like" data-show-faces="false" data-share="false"></div>        </div>
        <div class="blog__author-description subtext">
          Posted Nov 02, 2011        </div>
